findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInAccount() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops that can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the excluded addresses list is too long.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to include or exclude from rewards, change fee receiver address, and modify tax, burn, and charity fees.
